title: FULL SHOW: We Talk With Jo Koy, Mysonne, Talks Tory Lanez & More
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Talk With Jo Koy, Mysonne, Talks Tory Lanez & More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we are joined by friend of the show and comedian, Jo Koy. We talk everything from his latest career moves to his very public and amicable breakup with Chelsea Handler. Later on we have rapper Mysonne, A.T. Mitchell & Angelo Pinto to talk gun violence, lyrics In Court,  & community unity. During Rumors Yee reports on the August Alsina and Tory Lanez altercation and Charla gives us todays Donkey. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
